<H1><FONT SIZE="5">Company Overview</FONT></H1>

<P ALIGN="left"><IMG SRC="/images/haggerty.jpg" ALIGN="right" HSPACE="8"> <FONT SIZE="-1">Welcome to Western Digital Corporation's Internet
home page and to the world of information storage products and
services. Our company is a leader in this exciting industry, and
my thirteen thousand associates and I are eager for you to learn about
it.</FONT></P>

<P ALIGN="left"><FONT SIZE="-1">Western Digital was founded in 1970 as a
specialized semiconductor manufacturer. Today, we are an industry
leader in information storage management, providing a broad array
of hard disk drives for portable, personal and enterprise-wide
computing. We supply hard drives to many of the world's leading
PC manufacturers, and provide replacement and add-on data storage
products to the consumer market through resellers. We're proud
that some of the most renowned names in PC manufacturing have
made Western Digital their number one choice for hard drives. Now
we invite you to do the same.</FONT></P>

<P><FONT SIZE="-1">We are intensely quality-minded people. Ours is the first
U.S.-headquartered, multinational company to have been awarded
ISO 9001 registration company-wide, linking all Western
Digital organizations with a consistent global standard for
quality processes.</FONT></P>

<P><FONT SIZE="-1">Explore Western Digital's products, our service and support
capabilities, our financial performance, our employment
opportunities, and other aspects of this 27-year old leader in
information storage products and services. Welcome to Western
Digital.</FONT></P>

<P><FONT SIZE="-1"><B>Chuck Haggerty</B></FONT><B><BR>
<FONT SIZE="-1">
Chairman, President, and Chief Executive Officer <BR>
</FONT></B><FONT SIZE="-1"></FONT></P>
